INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES("74", "1", "2015-02-25 11:09:37", "2015-02-25 11:09:37", "[vegas id=16 fade=3000 delay=4000 overlay= arrows=yes autoplay=yes poster=no]\r\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><strong>SERVICES</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\">[ezcol_1quarter]</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px; text-align: left;\">Nicky Murray Design offers exclusive services for:</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px; text-align: left;\">• Complete residential and commercial project management\r\n• Full design, space and lighting schemes\r\n• Bespoke furniture and soft furnishings\r\n• Garden landscaping</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px; text-align: left;\">Each project is split into five main elements: Briefing, Concept Ideas and Development, Procurement, Fit Out and Final Dressing. These in turn are divided into different phases to allow the Nicky Murray Design team to fully grasp the client’s tastes and aspirations for the overall finish.</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px; text-align: left;\">In its first stages of Concept Ideas the team use a range of inspirational imagery, sketches and material palettes to engage the client and begin to bring the scheme to life. As the project moves into Development, the design process progresses into a more refined and developed perspective. The client will meet with the team several times during this period to explore all of the ideas in the proposed layout.</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px; text-align: left;\">Once the client has confirmed the design and space concepts, the Nicky Murray Design team will move into Procurement. This phase includes liaising with suppliers, travelling to choose the perfect mediums and materials, while ensuring all products are continuously monitored and quality checked. During Fit Out and Final Dressing the team will oversee each contractor and supplier to ensure a high standard of finish.</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\">[/ezcol_1quarter] [ezcol_1quarter]</p>\r\n<p s