INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES("283", "1", "2015-03-18 10:45:31", "2015-03-18 10:45:31", "[vegas id=208 fade=3000 delay=4000 overlay= arrows=yes autoplay=yes poster=no]\r\n\r\n[ezcol_1quarter]\r\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><strong>WELCOME TO NICKY MURRAY DESIGN</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-223\" src=\"http://welivedthedream.com/dev/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/divider_2.jpg\" alt=\"divider_2\" width=\"800\" height=\"20\" /></p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h5 class=\"articleCaption\" style=\"text-align: justify; padding-left: 30px;\">Known for her bold, confident designs as much as her enthusiasm and passion for her chosen field, the co-founder and creative visionary behind recently established Liberty Designs, Nicky brings over 15 years to the new endeavor.</h5>\r\n<h5 style=\"text-align: justify; padding-left: 30px;\">Experienced with both residential and commercial properties internationally, the London-based designer draws inspiration from all aspects of life from her exotic travels to attending fashion and trade shows. With an aptitude for \"getting inside her clients\' heads,\" the intrepid adventurer consistently delivers extraordinary interiors that dare to be different.</h5>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h5 style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><strong>DESIGN TEAM</strong></h5>\r\n<h5 style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><a href=\"http://welivedthedream.com/dev/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/divider_2.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-223\" src=\"http://welivedthedream.com/dev/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/divider_2.jpg\" alt=\"divider_2\" width=\"800\" height=\"20\" /></a></h5>\r\n<h5 style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><strong>Nicky Murray - Founder &amp; Owner</strong></h5>\r\n<h5 class=\"articleCaption\" style=\"padding-left: 30px; text-align: justify;\"><img class=\" size-thumbnail wp-image-202 alignleft\" src=\"http://welivedthedream.com/dev/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/nicky_profile-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"nicky_profile\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" />Known for her bold, confident designs as much as her enthusiasm and passion for her chosen field, the co-founder and creative visionary behind recently established Liberty Designs, Nicky brings over 15 years to the new endeavor.</h5>\r\n<h5 style=\"padding-left: 30px; text-align: justify;\">Experienced with both residential and commercial properties internationally, the London-based designer draws inspiration from all aspects of life from her exotic travels to attending fashion and trade shows. With an aptitude for \"getting inside her clients\' heads,\" the intrepid adventurer consistently delivers extraordinary interiors that dare to be different.</h5>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h5 style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><strong>Lucie Sadakova - Design Assistant</strong></h5>\r\n<h5 class=\"articleCaption\" style=\"text-align: justify; padding-left: 30px;\"><a href=\"http://welivedthedream.com/dev/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/lucie.jpg\"><img class=\" size-thumbnail wp-image-203 alignleft\" src=\"http://welivedthedream.com/dev/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/lucie-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"lucie\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" /></a>Lucie Sadakova works closely with Nicky Murray in the development of design ideas and solutions that respond to clients’ styles and needs. Her working sketches and technical drawing bring the ideas into sharper focus and help clients visualize what the final product will look like. Lucie is also responsible for ensuring a smooth and systematically organized process is in place for all projects. Truly passionate about the craft of interior design, Lucie has launched a personal blog on which she regularly posts articles about design products and trends.</h5>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h5 style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><strong>Robert Kent - Design Assistant</strong></h5>\r\n<h5 class=\"articleCaption\" style=\"text-align: justify; padding-left: 30px;\"><img class=\"alignleft wp-image-190 size-thumbnail\" src=\"http://welivedthedream.com/dev/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/12198090531909861341man-silhouette.svg_.hi_-150x150.png\" alt=\"12198090531909861341man silhouette.svg.hi\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" />Robert boasts 8 years of commercial interior architectural experience across a range of disciplines, 6 years of residential design.This gives him a very strong experience in both fields combined. His background experience is very much influenced by his training, working with some of the worlds leading design companies such as HOK, and Gensler. Previous clients include Apple, Cisco, Clifford Chance to name a few.</h5>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h5 style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><strong>Andraya Smith - Design Assistant</strong></h5>\r\n<h5 class=\"articleCaption\" style=\"text-align: justify; padding-left: 30px;\"><img class=\"alignleft wp-image-190 size-thumbnail\" src=\"http://welivedthedream.com/dev/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/12198090531909861341man-silhouette.svg_.hi_-150x150.png\" alt=\"12198090531909861341man silhouette.svg.hi\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" />After studying fashion in both London and Tokyo, Andraya Smith returned to the United States to pursue a career in fashion. In Miami, she successfully worked as a buyer and stylist for Miami’s top clothing boutiques and maga zines, but eventually the pull of the great city of London brought her back to the United Kingdom. In 2007, she decided to follow her life-long passion for interior design. It was a natural fit that enabled her to draw on the things that inspire her most, including travel, architecture, fashion, and beautiful objects.</h5>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h5 style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><strong>VJ Hirani - Design Assistant</strong></h5>\r\n<h5 class=\"articleCaption\" style=\"text-align: justify; padding-left: 30px;\"><img class=\"alignleft wp-image-190 size-thumbnail\" src=\"http://welivedthedream.com/dev/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/12198090531909861341man-silhouette.svg_.hi_-150x150.png\" alt=\"12198090531909861341man silhouette.svg.hi\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" />Known for her bold, confident designs as much as her enthusiasm and passion for her chosen field, the co-founder and creative visionary behind recently established Liberty Designs, Nicky brings over 15 years to the new endeavor.</h5>\r\n<h5 style=\"text-align: justify; padding-left: 30px;\">Experienced with both residential and commercial properties internationally, the London-based designer draws inspiration from all aspects of life from her exotic travels to attending fashion and trade shows. With an aptitude for \"getting inside her clients\' heads,\" the intrepid adventurer consistently delivers extraordinary interiors that dare to be different.</h5>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h5 style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><strong>Craig Proudfoot - Project Director</strong></h5>\r\n<h5 class=\"articleCaption\" style=\"padding-left: 30px; text-align: justify;\"><a href=\"http://welivedthedream.com/dev/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/3ce1a25.jpg\"><img class=\" size-thumbnail wp-image-214 alignleft\" src=\"http://welivedthedream.com/dev/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/3ce1a25-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"3ce1a25\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" /></a>Craig has worked for major architectural practices in both Edinburgh and Antwerp. He has a versatile skills base with over fifteen years experience in various aspects of construction management, project development, design &amp; planning. He spent 5 years as a project co-ordinator for a multi award winning residential development company, calling on architectural and project management skills to orchestrate and deliver efficient construction programmes and high quality building products. Craig holds a bachelor of Arhcitecture (Hons) and diploma in architecture.</h5>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h5 style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><strong>Douglas Mackay - Digital Designer</strong></h5>\r\n<h5 class=\"articleCaption\" style=\"text-align: justify; padding-left: 30px;\"><img class=\"alignleft wp-image-190 size-thumbnail\" src=\"http://welivedthedream.com/dev/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/12198090531909861341man-silhouette.svg_.hi_-150x150.png\" alt=\"12198090531909861341man silhouette.svg.hi\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" />Douglas has over 15 years’ experience in the creative industries. His main skills lie in brand identity &amp; development although he has a wealth of knowledge in print, online media and film which he has produced for a wide variety of Edinburgh &amp; London based companies. Douglas is also a professional design consultant specialising in creative direction and holds a BSc (Hons) in Interactive Media Design.</h5>\r\n<h5 style=\"text-align: justify; padding-left: 30px;\">[/ezcol_1quarter] [ezcol_3quarter_end]</h5>\r\n<h5></h5>\r\n<h5></h5>\r\n<h5></h5>\r\n[/ezcol_3quarter_end]", "", "", "inherit", "open", "open", "", "61-revision-v1", "", "", "2015-03-18 10:45:31", "2015-03-18 10:45:31", "", "61", "http://welivedthedream.com/dev/61-revision-v1/", "0", "revision", "", "0");
