INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES("480", "2", "2015-12-02 13:14:05", "2015-12-02 13:14:05", "[vegas id=208 fade=3000 delay=4000 overlay= arrows=yes autoplay=yes poster=no]\r\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\">[ezcol_1quarter]</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><strong>DESIGN TEAM</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><a href=\"http://welivedthedream.com/dev/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/divider_2.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-223\" src=\"http://welivedthedream.com/dev/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/divider_2.jpg\" alt=\"divider_2\" width=\"800\" height=\"20\" /></a></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><strong>Nicky Murray - Founder &amp; Owner</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"articleCaption\" style=\"padding-left: 30px; text-align: justify;\"><img class=\" size-thumbnail wp-image-202 alignleft\" src=\"http://www.nickymurraydesign.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/thumb_nicky_profile-150x150_1024-1.jpg\" alt=\"nicky_profile\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px; text-align: left;\">Experienced with both residential and commercial properties internationally, the London-based designer draws inspiration from all aspects of life, from her exotic travels to attending fashion and trade shows. With an aptitude for \"getting inside her clients\' heads,\" the intrepid adventurer consistently delivers extraordinary interiors that dare to be different.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><strong>Lucie Sadakova - Senior Designer</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"articleCaption\" style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><a href=\"http://www.nickymurraydesign.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/lucie-150x1501.jpg\"><img class=\" size-thumbnail wp-image-203 alignleft\" src=\"http://welivedthedream.com/dev/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/lucie-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"lucie\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" /></a>Lucie works closely with Nicky Murray in the development of design ideas and solutions that respond to clients’ styles and needs. Her working sketches and technical drawing bring the ideas into sharper focus and help clients visualize what the final product will look like. Lucie is also responsible for ensuring a smooth and systematically organized process is in place for all projects. Truly passionate about the craft of interior design, Lucie has launched a personal blog on which she regularly posts articles about design products and trends.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><strong>Robert Kent - Senior Designer</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"articleCaption\" style=\"padding-left: 30px; text-align: left;\"><img class=\" wp-image-349 size-thumbnail alignleft\" src=\"http://www.nickymurraydesign.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/thumb_robert_kent-150x150_1024.jpg\" alt=\"robert_kent\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" />Robert boasts 8 years of commercial interior architectural experience across a range of disciplines, 6 years of residential design.This gives him a very strong experience in both fields combined. His background experience is very much influenced by his training, working with some of the worlds leading design companies such as HOK, and Gensler. Previous clients include Apple, Cisco, Clifford Chance to name a few.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><strong>Craig Proudfoot - Project Director</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"articleCaption\" style=\"padding-left: 30px; text-align: left;\"><a href=\"http://www.nickymurraydesign.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/3ce1a25-150x1501.jpg\"><img class=\" size-thumbnail wp-image-214 alignleft\" src=\"http://welivedthedream.com/dev/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/3ce1a25-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"3ce1a25\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" /></a>Craig has worked for major architectural practices in both Edinburgh and Antwerp. He has a versatile skills base with over fifteen years experience in various aspects of construction management, project development, design &amp; planning. He spent 5 years as a project co-ordinator for a multi award winning residential development company, calling on architectural and project management skills to orchestrate and deliver efficient construction programmes and high quality building products. Craig holds a bachelor of Architecture (Hons) and diploma in architecture.</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><strong>Samantha Emlick</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"articleCaption\" style=\"padding-left: 30px; text-align: left;\"><a href=\"http://www.nickymurraydesign.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/SAMMY.jpeg\"><img class=\" size-thumbnail wp-image-214 alignleft\" src=\"http://welivedthedream.com/dev/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/3ce1a25-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"3ce1a25\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" /></a>Samantha boasts both a business degree and diploma from the Conde Nast College of Fashion in London, providing her with invaluable foundations of design and business acumen.Following Samantha’s career in fashion, her natural ability and wealth of knowledge towards design allows her to predict and identify up and coming trends, providing a unique and contemporary edge to all of our designs. \r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><strong>Emma Wither</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"articleCaption\" style=\"padding-left: 30px; text-align: left;\"><a href=\"http://www.nickymurraydesign.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/EMMA-2.jpeg\"><img class=\" size-thumbnail wp-image-214 alignleft\" src=\"http://welivedthedream.com/dev/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/3ce1a25-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"3ce1a25\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" /></a>After graduating with distinction in her Masters of Innovation, Creativity and Entrepreneurship at Newcastle University, Emma was keen to further explore her creative abilities, and commenced her course with KLC to complete her Diploma in Interior Design. Emma’s aptitude to combine her artistic finesse with attentiveness to research a development in intricate detail brings a wealth of knowledge to each project.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"></p>\r\n<p class=\"articleCaption\" style=\"padding-left: 30px; text-align: left;\"></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; padding-left: 30px;\">[/ezcol_1quarter] [ezcol_3quarter_end]</p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n[/ezcol_3quarter_end]", "", "", "inherit", "open", "open", "", "61-revision-v1", "", "", "2015-12-02 13:14:05", "2015-12-02 13:14:05", "", "61", "http://www.nickymurraydesign.com/61-revision-v1/", "0", "revision", "", "0");
