i award winning residential development company, calling on architectural and project management skills to orchestrate and deliver efficient construction programmes and high quality building products. Craig holds a bachelor of Architecture (Hons) and diploma in architecture.</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><strong>Samantha Emlick - designer</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"articleCaption\" style=\"padding-left: 30px; text-align: left;\"><a href=\"http://www.nickymurraydesign.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/SAMMY-3.jpeg\"><img class=\" size-thumbnail wp-image-214 alignleft\" src=\"http://www.nickymurraydesign.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/SAMMY-3.jpeg\" alt=\"3ce1a25\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" /></a>Samantha boasts both a business degree and diploma from the Conde Nast College of Fashion in London, providing her with invaluable foundations of design and business acumen.Following Samantha’s career in fashion, her natural ability and wealth of knowledge towards design allows her to predict and identify up and coming trends, providing a unique and contemporary edge to all of our designs. \r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><strong>Emma Withe - designer</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"articleCaption\" style=\"padding-left: 30px; text-align: left;\"><a href=\"http://www.nickymurraydesign.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/1497509_10153399956484570_5138263032494687234_n.jpeg\"><img class=\" size-thumbnail wp-image-214 alignleft\" src=\"http://www.nickymurraydesign.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/1497509_10153399956484570_5138263032494687234_n.jpeg\" alt=\"3ce1a25\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" /></a>After graduating with distinction in her Masters of Innovation, Creativity and Entrepreneurship at Newcastle University, Emma was keen to further explore her creative abilities, and commenced her course with KLC to complete her Diploma in Interior Design. Emma’s aptitude to combine her artistic finesse with attentiveness to research a development in intricate detail brings a wealth of knowledge to each project.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"></p>\r\n<p class=\"articleCaption\" style=\"padding-left: 30px; text-align: left;\"></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; padding-left: 30px;\">[/ezcol_1quarter] [ezcol_3quarter_end]</p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n[/ezcol_3quarter_end]", "", "", "inherit", "open", "open", "", "61-revision-v1", "", "", "2015-12-03 18:33:10", "2015-12-03 18:33:10", "", "61", "http://www.nickymurraydesign.com/61-revision-v1/", "0", "revision", "", "0");
